OL,3,CUK heatwave in numbers: The six
OL,4,C'unprecedented' stats
OL,6,FBy Weather Presenter Nick Miller
OL,8,FThis week has seen an extraordinary
OL,9,Fand historic heatwave which has
OL,10,Fshattered some long-standing weather
OL,11,Frecords across much of England and
OL,12,FWales for this time of year.
OL,14,FHere's a break down of the
OL,15,Ftemperatures and new statistics we've
OL,16,Fseen over the past few days.
OL,18,FUK temperature record
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
