PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779901592
OL,3,CUK heatwave in numbers: The six
OL,4,C'unprecedented' stats
OL,6,FThe highest temperature was recorded
OL,7,Fat London's Kew Gardens - which hit
OL,8,F35.1C on Tuesday. That's not only a
OL,9,Fnew UK record for May but it is also
OL,10,Fhigher than Kew's record June
OL,11,Ftemperature.
OL,13,FWales temperature record
OL,15,FWales also set a new national May
OL,16,Frecord on Tuesday reaching 32.9C in
OL,17,FCardiff. Both the Wales and the new UK
OL,18,FMay high at Kew broke their previous
OL,19,Frecords by 2.3 degrees, that's an
OL,20,Fastonishing margin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
