OL,3,CUK heatwave in numbers: The six
OL,4,C'unprecedented' stats
OL,6,FNight temperature record
OL,8,FThe nights have also been record-
OL,9,Fbreaking. On Tuesday night, Camborne
OL,10,Fin Cornwall set a new May minimum
OL,11,Ftemperature record falling no lower
OL,12,Fthan 21.4C.
OL,14,FUnprecedented 'tropical nights'
OL,16,FThere have also been a number of
OL,17,F'tropical nights' - this is when the
OL,18,Ftemperature does not fall below 20
OL,19,Fdegrees overnight. This is
OL,20,Funprecedented for the UK so early in
OL,21,Fthe year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
