OL,3,CUK heatwave in numbers: The six
OL,4,C'unprecedented' stats
OL,6,FRecords broken at more than 150 sites
OL,7,Fin the UK
OL,9,FThe extent of the May heat across the
OL,10,FUK has also been significant.
OL,12,FAs of Tuesday, 163 separate Met Office
OL,13,Fweather observation sites recorded new
OL,14,Frecord high temperatures for the
OL,15,Fmonth, the furthest north is at
OL,16,FInverbervie in Scotland.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, 99 sites have seen record
OL,19,Fwarm May nights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
