OL,3,CUK heatwave in numbers: The six
OL,4,C'unprecedented' stats
OL,6,FRecords three times more likely to be
OL,7,Fbroken
OL,9,FBreaking the May record high is now
OL,10,Fthree times more likely with natural
OL,11,Fweather patterns than it was before
OL,12,Fthe industrial revolution, according
OL,13,Fto The Met Office.
OL,15,FIt also says the UK's new May top
OL,16,Ftemperature now means that since 2003
OL,17,Fthe UK has set new monthly records in
OL,18,F7 out of the 12 months of the year as
OL,19,Four climate warms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
